      "setOfCodes": "0:Not critical;1:Critical;",
      "helpText": "The value of this field is a flag that indicates whether or not the current error is a \"critical\" one. When an error is \"critical\", a e-mail message will be transmitted to the Imaging Team in Silver Spring. ",
